  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:9",
      "text": "--engine=HOST[:port]",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:10",
      "text": "tractor-engine 运行所在的 hostname[:port]，默认值为 tractor-engine，通常是一个 DNS alias；默认 port 为 80。如果未给出此选项，blade 还会查找名为 TRACTOR_ENGINE 的 environment variable，用作 host:port 说明。如果显式设置和环境变量都不存在，blade 会尝试通过本地 nameserver 解析 hostname \"tractor-engine\"。如果该名称",
      "ascii_letters": 131,
      "cjk_chars": 65
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:13",
      "text": "engine discovery",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:17",
      "text": "此 blade 监听 admin queries 的 port，默认值为 9005；使用 0（zero）可让 operating system 选择一个空闲 port。blade 会把给定 port 注册到 engine。注意，该 port 必须能穿过 blade host 上可能存在的 firewall，因此在使用 firewalls 时，像 9005 这样的固定值比随机值更合适。可以使用 '--listen=addr:port' 选择指定的本地 network interface。",
      "ascii_letters": 119,
      "cjk_chars": 70
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:18",
      "text": "--hname=HOSTNAME",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:22",
      "text": "记录 INFO 及以上 log level。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:24",
      "text": "记录 DEBUG 及以上 log level。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:26",
      "text": "记录 TRACE 及以上 log level。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:28",
      "text": "记录 WARNING 及以上 log level，这是默认值。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:31",
      "text": "只记录 CRITICAL log level。",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:32",
      "text": "--log=LOGFILE",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:33",
      "text": "tractor-blade activity log file，达到 25MB 时自动轮转。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:34",
      "text": "--logrotate=NNN",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:35",
      "text": "指定 log-rotation threshold，单位为 megabytes。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:36",
      "text": "--logconfig=LOGCONFIG",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:38",
      "text": "logging-module",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:40",
      "text": "CmdOutputLogging",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:43",
      "text": "记录 blade 启动的每条 command 的实际 command line 和 environment。",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:46",
      "text": "--zone=ZONE",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:47",
      "text": "用于 'dirmap' indexing 的 zone name。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:48",
      "text": "--nimby=NAME",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:50",
      "text": "--slots=SLOTS",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:51",
      "text": "最大并发 slot 数；覆盖 blade.config 中通常的 Capacity parameter MaxSlots；使用 '0' 可把 slot count 设置为系统 CPU cores 的数量。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:53",
      "text": "（仅 unix）让 blade process 脱离 controlling terminal session，并自动在后台运行，从而作为 system daemon 执行。",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:54",
      "text": "--supersede",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:56",
      "text": "--profile=NAME",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:57",
      "text": "指定 blade.config 中要使用的 blade profile name，跳过通常的匹配条件；仅用于 testing scenarios。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:58",
      "text": "--env=ENVFILE",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:59",
      "text": "应用程序 override environment settings 的文件名（例如从 printenv 捕获）。注意：environment settings 通常通过 blade.config 中具名的 EnvKeys collections 定义。",
      "ascii_letters": 83,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:60",
      "text": "--pythonhome=PYTHONHOME",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:61",
      "text": "为 Tractor 启动的 Python programs 设置 PYTHONHOME。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:62",
      "text": "--ld_library_path=LDPATH",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:63",
      "text": "为 Tractor 启动的 programs 设置 LD_LIBRARY_PATH。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:64",
      "text": "--dyld_framework_path=PATH",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:65",
      "text": "为 Tractor 启动的 programs 设置 LD_FRAMEWORK_PATH。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:66",
      "text": "--no-sigint",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:67",
      "text": "中断 active tasks 时，先用 SIGTERM 而不是 SIGINT 发起 task termination attempts（仅 unix）。",
      "ascii_letters": 51,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:68",
      "text": "--killdelay=SECS",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:69",
      "text": "清扫 active subprocesses 时，从 SIGNINT 升级到 SIGTERM 再到 SIGKILL 之间等待的秒数。",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:70",
      "text": "--progresslimit=NSECS",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:71",
      "text": "限制 percent-done updates 的发送频率，两次发送之间至少等待 NSECS seconds。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:72",
      "text": "--startupdelay=SECS",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:73",
      "text": "service boot 之后、继续执行 blade startup actions 之前的 delay。",
      "ascii_letters": 35,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:74",
      "text": "--minsleep=MINSLEEP",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:75",
      "text": "最小 idle sleep interval，单位为 seconds。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:76",
      "text": "--maxsleep=MAXSLEEP",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "3b62f4738d:77",
      "text": "最大 idle sleep interval，单位为 seconds。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
